-- Harbinger Capital Buys Old Mutual's U.S. Life Operations for $350 Million
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-08-06T06:03:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/harbinger-capital-buys-old-mutual-s-u-s-life-operations-for-350-million.html

          
          
             Old Mutual Plc said it has agreed to
sell its U.S. life operations to Harbinger Capital Partners for
$350 million.  
          
          


  


        